      <title>特朗普任命前民主党人加巴德为情报局局长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-taps-former-democrat-gabbard-for-intelligence-director</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普选择前美国众议员、曾任民主党总统候选人的塔尔西·加巴德担任国家情报总监，提拔一位忠诚分子和对乌克兰支持的怀疑者来协调国家间谍机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-taps-former-democrat-gabbard-for-intelligence-director</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 20:37:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命忠诚的议员马特·盖茨 (Matt Gaetz) 为司法部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-taps-loyalist-lawmaker-matt-gaetz-for-attorney-general</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他提名马特·盖茨担任司法部长，任命一位坚定的保守派议员重塑美国执法部门并执行他在移民、犯罪和热点社会问题上的议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-taps-loyalist-lawmaker-matt-gaetz-for-attorney-general</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 20:33:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党大获全胜为促进石油和天然气开发开辟道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/republican-sweep-opens-way-to-boost-oil-and-gas-development</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在确保对国会和白宫的统一控制后，共和党准备为扩大化石燃料开发、撤销拜登时代的环境法规和限制拜登总统签署的气候法铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/republican-sweep-opens-way-to-boost-oil-and-gas-development</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 20:22:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OMV 因 2022 年天然气纠纷从俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司获得 2.3 亿欧元赔偿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/omv-wins-230-million-award-from-gazprom-on-2022-gas-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OMV AG 表示，该公司已从俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司 PJSC 获得了 2.3 亿欧元（2.43 亿美元）的奖励，外加与 2022 年天然气交付相关的成本和利息，这将提高利润，但也会冒着未来从俄罗斯采购的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/omv-wins-230-million-award-from-gazprom-on-2022-gas-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 20:22:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果与国际货币基金组织就 29 亿美元新融资达成一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/congo-and-imf-to-agree-on-2-9-billion-in-new-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织工作人员同意支持这个中非国家的两个新的贷款项目，刚果民主共和国将在未来三年内获得近 29 亿美元的融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/congo-and-imf-to-agree-on-2-9-billion-in-new-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 20:19:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院阻挠议事将如何迫使特朗普与民主党谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/how-senate-filibuster-will-force-trump-to-deal-with-democrats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着当选总统唐纳德·特朗普及其共和党同僚在 11 月 5 日的选举中赢得白宫和参众两院的控制权，民主党将拥有一个制衡多数党权力的重要工具：阻挠议事。这是参议院少数党享有的特权，要求进行永无止境的辩论以阻止立法，而立法必须得到参议院和众议院的批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/how-senate-filibuster-will-force-trump-to-deal-with-democrats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 20:13:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普赢得共和党三连胜，共和党保留众议院多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/republicans-keep-control-of-us-house-in-power-sweep</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党在美国众议院保持微弱多数，使得唐纳德·特朗普及其政党统一控制民选政府部门，并限制了对新任总统权力的潜在限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/republicans-keep-control-of-us-house-in-power-sweep</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 19:20:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>检方寻求禁止勒庞参选法国总统 或将无缘竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/le-pen-risks-missing-presidential-race-as-prosecutors-seek-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国右翼国民联盟党领袖玛丽娜·勒庞面临错过法国下一届总统竞选的风险，此前，贪污案审判结束后，检察官要求立即禁止她五年内参加竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/le-pen-risks-missing-presidential-race-as-prosecutors-seek-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 19:02:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命卢比奥为国务卿，新团队初具规模</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-builds-out-white-house-staff-as-he-returns-to-washington</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普确认，他有意提名佛罗里达州参议员马尔科·卢比奥担任国务卿，提名一位曾经的竞争对手担任高级内阁职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-builds-out-white-house-staff-as-he-returns-to-washington</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 16:21:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登和特朗普在白宫会晤中承诺实现“平稳”过渡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-biden-to-meet-as-trump-names-key-picks-to-reshape-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普周三会见了共和党总统乔·拜登，这是拜登四年前混乱离任后首次返回白宫。]]></description>
